AWD Porsche 964 track car? Yes. Definitely.

Published on Aug 12, 2014
The sound of this car is phenomenal. 

When you think of of a classic Porsche, you predictably think, "911", but you probably don't think "964", or "AWD". Certainly not if you want to build a track car. 

But if you're Larry Kosilla, who has worked himself ragged for years, and lives in the northeastern U.S., you don't want to own a dream car that you can't drive when it's snowy out. He wanted something he can drive any time he wants, and take to the track, anytime he wants. 

The result of his idea is astounding.
